      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Aaron Tay</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"//www.library20.com/profiles/profile/show?id=AaronTay&amp;xg_source=activity\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/76/Aarontay.jpg/300px-Aarontay.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"268\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/7/76/Aarontay.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Aarontay.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Aaron Tay <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Aaron Tay Chee Hsien</b>,<br />\na Singaporean Resource Librarian at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_University_of_Singapore\">National University of Singapore</a>, computer chess enthusiast and early <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> promoter. \nHe wrote computer chess articles on various topics <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, along with his <i>FAQ on Winboard and Chess Engines</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> hosted by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aaron_Tay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=155201\">Question about EPD</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aaron Tay</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=200064\">Looking for a position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aaron Tay</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_1977\" title=\"WCCC 1977\">WCCC 1977</a>, <a href=\"/Duchess\" title=\"Duchess\">Duchess</a> - <a href=\"/Kaissa\" title=\"Kaissa\">Kaissa</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aaron_Tay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.library20.com/profiles/profile/show?id=AaronTay&amp;xg_source=activity\">Aaron Tay's Page - Library 2.0</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horizonchess.com/FAQ/Winboard/index.html\">FAQ on Winboard and Chess Engines</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horizonchess.com/FAQ/Winboard/article.html\">Chess engines articles by Aaron Tay</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horizonchess.com/FAQ/Winboard/computer.html\">Beginner's Guide to running Computer Chess Tournament</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/aarontay/status/15023914670\">Twitter / Aaron Tay: Let's play Chess ...</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aaron_Tay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.library20.com/profiles/profile/show?id=AaronTay&amp;xg_source=activity\">Aaron Tay's Page - Library 2.0</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horizonchess.com/FAQ/Winboard/article.html\">Chess engines articles by Aaron Tay</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horizonchess.com/FAQ/Winboard/index.html\">FAQ on Winboard and Chess Engines</a> is by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301133944\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6126-0!canonica